<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f7f7f7;
            padding: 0;
            margin: 0;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .header {
            background-color: #003366;
            color: #ffffff;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .content {
            background-color: #ffffff;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 20px;
            color: #777;
        }
    </style>
    <title></title>
</head>
<body>
<div class="container">
    <div class="header">
        <h1>Welcome to Desta Touring!</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
        <p>Dear <%= user.name %>,</p>
        <p>
            Congratulations! Your account has been successfully verified and you are now ready to start your adventure
            with Desta Touring.
        </p>
        <p>
            We are thrilled to have you on board. Our app offers a wide range of tours and travel packages
            tailored to meet your desires for exploration and adventure. Whether you're seeking a serene getaway or an
            action-packed excursion,
            we've got you covered.
        </p>
        <p>
            Here are a few tips to get you started:
        </p>
        <ul>
            <li>Explore our latest tour packages and find your perfect trip.</li>
            <li>Customize your travel experience with our flexible options.</li>
            <li>Stay updated with exclusive offers and promotions by keeping notifications on.</li>
            <li>Reach out to our support team anytime for assistance or inquiries.</li>
        </ul>
        <p>
            If you have any questions or need help planning your next trip, feel free to contact our support team
            at <%= supportEmail %>.
        </p>
        <p>
            Thank you for choosing Desta Touring. We can't wait to help you create unforgettable memories!
        </p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
        <p>Best regards,</p>
        <p>The Desta Touring Team</p>
    </div>
</div>

</body>
</html>